Choose the number of times price crosses over the midnight price before taking a position or use it to create alerts for crossing the midnight price. Adjust your timeframe for exiting the position. You can confirm momentum with consecutive candle closes and you can add a trailing stop or a break even profit strategy. No signals generated from this script should be considered advice for investment or trading. Created with Gemini.
